    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 18th level, you have an uncanny knack for succeeding when you need to.</p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.zI0nbW3k0im9oCc9]{Stroke of Luck: Attack}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.kRXYFpo8k4PrEZQ9]{Stroke of Luck: Ability Check}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.m5Wofh4lrZQTi5Ui]{Stroke of Luck: Saving Throw}</li></ul><p>You may replace a single ability check, attack roll and saving throw once each. Once you do so, you may not do so again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
